(define/contract (find-high-access-employees access_times)
  (-> (listof (listof string?)) (listof string?))
  (define (time-difference time1 time2)
    (let ([hour1 (string->number (substring time1 0 2))]
          [minute1 (string->number (substring time1 2 4))]
          [hour2 (string->number (substring time2 0 2))]
          [minute2 (string->number (substring time2 2 4))])
      (+ (- hour2 hour1) (/ (- minute2 minute1) 60.0))))
  (define (is-within-hour? times)
    (for/or ([i (in-range 0 (- (length times) 2))])
            (for/or ([j (in-range (+ i 1) (length times))])
                    (< (time-difference (list-ref times i) (list-ref times j)) 1))))
  (define (filter-high-access-employees employees)
    (let ([grouped (make-hash)])
      (for ([employee (in-list employees)])
           (let ([name (first employee)]
                 [time (second employee)])
             (hash-update! grouped name (lambda (times) (cons time times)) '())))
      (hash-map grouped (lambda (name times)
                          (if (and (> (length times) 2) (is-within-hour? (sort times string<?)))
                              name
                              #f)))))
  (filter-map identity (filter-high-access-employees access_times)))
